rows.label: qst200911_msg001
rows.name:
Otto! You're back late! What was
the holdup?

rows.label: qst200911_msg002
rows.name:
I, er, got into a spot of trouble,
you could say. These fine people
here managed to help me out.

rows.label: qst200911_msg003
rows.name:
Speaking of, didn't you say you had
business with me?

rows.label: qst200911_msg004
rows.name:
That's right! We wanted to ask for
your help!

rows.label: qst200911_msg005
rows.name:
The windmill over at Tilly Bakery
broke down!

rows.label: qst200911_msg006
rows.name:
They can't open the shop unless
they've got flour to work with, so they
asked us to fetch you to fix the mill!

rows.label: qst200911_msg007
rows.name:
Ahh, I see, I see. Sure, I can take
a look at it.

rows.label: qst200911_msg009
rows.name:
Least I could do for someone who
just saved my life, isn't it? Tell you
what, I'll even do it for free.

rows.label: qst200911_msg014
rows.name:
I'll head over to Tilly's now then.
Come along later if you like.
